title: Planned roadworks in Devon and Cornwall: weekly summary for Monday 12 October - Sunday 18 ...
text: ( Source : Highways England ) Devon A30 Junction 31 Exeter : survey work From Monday 12 October to Friday 16 October there will be a closure of the link road from A30 to A38 southbound from 9pm to 6am for surveys. Diversion via A377, B3123
